# AI Provider API Keys
# You need at least one API key to use RADFLOW

# Google Gemini (Default - Recommended for full feature support including grounding and image generation)
# Get your key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Alternative: Use generic API_KEY environment variable
# This will be used as fallback for the default provider
API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Additional providers can be configured in the Settings panel:
# - OpenAI: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# - Anthropic Claude: https://console.anthropic.com/
# - OpenRouter: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# - Perplexity: https://www.perplexity.ai/settings/api

# Note: Provider-specific features
# - Grounding (web search): Google Gemini only
# - Image generation: Google Gemini with Imagen models only
# - All providers support text generation tasks
